    <h2 class="text-3xl font-orbitron font-bold text-white mb-6">What is AI Automation for HR Onboarding?</h2>
    <p class="text-white mb-4">
      AI automation for HR onboarding is the application of artificial intelligence to streamline and enhance the process of integrating new employees into an organization. It marks a significant evolution from manual, paper-based systems to intelligent, adaptive workflows that manage everything from initial paperwork to personalized training schedules.
    </p>
    <p class="text-white">
      This technology automates repetitive administrative tasks, personalizes the new hire journey, and ensures seamless integration with existing Human Resource Information Systems (HRIS). The scope is vast, covering automated document processing, compliance management, system access provisioning, and the delivery of customized training content.
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 my-8">
      <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 p-6 rounded-xl text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-2">68%</div>
        <p class="text-white">Of organizations now use AI in their hiring and onboarding processes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 p-6 rounded-xl text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-2">38%</div>
        <p class="text-white">Of HR decision-makers currently employ AI in their daily workflows.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 p-6 rounded-xl text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-2">92%</div>
        <p class="text-white">Of companies plan to increase their AI investments in the coming years.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-white">
      The market is rapidly transforming as businesses recognize the immense value of automating these critical functions. By leveraging AI, HR departments can create a more engaging, efficient, and error-free onboarding experience that sets employees up for long-term success.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-orbitron font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">Key Benefits of AI Automation for HR Onboarding</h2>
    <p class="text-white mb-4">
      Implementing AI automation in HR onboarding delivers substantial, measurable benefits across the organization. The most immediate impacts are significant cost and time savings. HR professionals report over $18,000 in annual savings, with onboarding time reduced by 40-60% as processes that once took a week are completed in a single day.
    </p>
    <p class="text-white">
      Beyond efficiency, AI dramatically improves the employee experience. Personalized onboarding paths lead to a 25% increase in employee involvement and contribute to an impressive 82% boost in new hire retention. This enhanced engagement translates directly to a 70% increase in productivity for effectively onboarded employees.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 p-6 rounded-xl my-8">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
