          <ol class="text-white space-y-2">
            <li><strong>1. Assess Needs:</strong> Define clear goals for automation and identify key pain points.</li>
            <li><strong>2. Select Vendor:</strong> Choose a platform that aligns with your technical and business requirements.</li>
            <li><strong>3. Plan Rollout:</strong> Develop a phased implementation plan with stakeholder training.</li>
            <li><strong>4. Measure & Optimize:</strong> Continuously track performance and gather feedback for improvement.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
